strings: <voice_0x01000E64><se_low>King of tricks: Is this not an unforgivable issue?
<voice_0x01000E65><se_low>King of tricks: Since I can remember...
<voice_0x01000E66><se_low>King of tricks: Agree! This is Arjuna's field!
<voice_0x01000E67><se_low>King of tricks: My daughter will marry the prince of the kingdom.
<voice_0x01000E68><se_low>King of tricks: if you find the magic mirror You will surely meet King Kravis and Prince Hamelis.
<voice_0x01000E69><se_low>King of tricks: The princess's current situation must be hidden!
<voice_0x01000E6A><se_low>King of tricks: If someone asks why you're here, pretend you're after a criminal named Dormago.
<voice_0x01000E6B><se_low>King of tricks: In fact, there was no way the princess and I were going to wear the same clothes to enter the kingdom.
<voice_0x01000E6C><se_low>King of tricks: Sleeper, thank you for fooling me.
<voice_0x01000E6D><se_low>King of tricks: Most importantly, you must find him as soon as possible and stop his plans.
<voice_0x01000E6E><se_low>King of tricks: Because of the curse of hell, my daughter must play cricket in heaven.
